		<div id="unique-entry-id-289" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">2009 Author Appearances</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Friday, 12 February 2010 </div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><img class="imageStyle" alt="vampirates" src="vampirates.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></div>Did you attend a Vampirate event last year?  Vampirate Central now has a list of them all.<br />Check out <a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/events/2009AuthorAppearances/" rel="external" title="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/events/2009AuthorAppearances/">www.vampirates.co.uk/events/2009AuthorAppearances</a><br /><br />For forthcoming events please see <a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/events/EventDates/" rel="external" title="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/events/EventDates/">www.vampirates.co.uk/events/EventDates</a><br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-285" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">West Midland Vampirates</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Wednesday, 03 February 2010 </div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><img class="imageStyle" alt="vampirates" src="vampirates.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></div>For anyone in West Midlands area of England, you may be interested in an event in Wolverhampton.  Justin Somper is appearing at the Colton Hills Community School Theatre on Thursday, 25 February 2010 from 19:00 - 21:00.<br /><br />Admission is free. Tickets are available from Waterstones bookshop and Central Children's Library Wolverhampton.<br /><br />Please see <a href="http://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=310280411207&ref=nf" rel="external" title="www.facebook.com/event">www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=310280411207&ref=nf </a>for more information.<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-278" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">The Stuff of Legend</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Monday, 01 February 2010 </div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><img class="imageStyle" alt="vampirates" src="vampirates.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></div><a href="http://www.jewishbookweek.com/2010/the-stuff-of-legend.php" rel="external" title="http://www.jewishbookweek.com">Jewish Book Week</a> on Sunday 7th March 2010 at 4.30pm to 6.30pm<br />Join award-winning writers Inbali Iserles and Justin Somper who will be talking about their worlds of adventure beyond the familiar time and spaces. Board Somper&rsquo;s ship of Vampirates (Vampires and pirates in one) and be the first to hear&nbsp;about his new book, Empire of the Night,&nbsp;or&nbsp; be drawn into Iserles&rsquo; modern day myths which bring exotic worlds to North London and even reveal the secret passages which can lead you&nbsp; there.  Recommended Age 8-12.  Royal National Hotel, London, WC1 0DG - &pound;5 in advance.<br />See <a href="http://www.jewishbookweek.com/2010/the-stuff-of-legend.php" rel="external" title="http://www.jewishbookweek.com">www.jewishbookweek.com/2010/the-stuff-of-legend.php</a> for more details.<br /></div></div>
